data.description: Location, convenience, practicality. This 3bedroom, 2bath, 2car garage single family home is minutes away from immediate shopping needs, schools, dining and entertainment, and close to Midpoint Bridge. It offers a split floor plan with a double door entry leading to a cozy family room with dining area. Both master and guest bath have dual sinks, walk-in closet in master. The functional kitchen has newer appliances, breakfast bar, eat-in-kitchen area that invites lots of natural sunlight. The covered and screened in Lanai is spacious enough to accommodate a large patio table and a grill. The open backyard is yours to design with ample room to accommodate a swimming pool. Schedule your showing today!
